{"tid":541950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周庭隊友致電選舉處被cut線","createTime":"2018-01-27T04:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T13:23:08.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c80665a722c8865bef0fffd59cbec719a35cd7","tid":541950,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"立法會補選提名期下周一結束，盛傳會被取消參選資格的香港眾志周庭及姚松炎，香港眾志傍晚於facebook上載一段電話錄音，指該黨多次嘗識聯絡選舉主任，但被民政事務處職員阻撓。錄音中，民政處職員稱選舉主任「宜家開緊會」，當眾志代表稱希望到民政署辦事處等候選舉主任，民政處職員以辦工時間只到六時推搪，又問「幾多人上來」。當眾志代表稱只有一個人，民政處職員即回應「得你一個人啫」，之後草草收線。香港眾志促選舉事務處和選舉主任盡快交代報名的情況，不要強行拖延確認周庭的參選資格。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎與周庭今日仍然如常落區，他們的團隊及多名民主派議員將於明天起一連兩日，發起「香港人要Plan A」行動，包括設立街站及周日舉行集會，呼籲市民誓保「Plan A」。<br />\n<br />\n參選港島區的周庭和參選九龍西的姚松炎，至今仍未獲確認參選資格，多份報章引述消息人士指二人將會被DQ。周、姚的競選團隊計劃周日在公民廣場外集會，呼籲市民保衞「Plan A」，「反對威權DQ、立即核淮候選人資格」。他們明日會在堅尼地城和銅鑼灣擺設反DQ街站。姚松炎指，報章引述的DQ消息毫無法律理據，而他本人索取的法律意見亦認為沒有DQ的理由，他會如常進行選舉工程。周庭亦指，不會被傳言影響，會如常擺街站落區。"},{"pid":"9e579328967bba918a06a2e8233a7d72e5f5d2b9","tid":541950,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"浸大校內外都受藍絲輿論打壓<br />\n連BU 學生去選都一樣DQ<br />\nBu 禍不單行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba09a2d40a8b69447e8506f617b86b1bae8680d5","tid":541950,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"政府咁撚串？"},{"pid":"5200aabb67408e96c1f3e30f6d3f57d6dc0a7877","tid":541950,"uid":36820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbc1e6e0b29a3cb94d5163ef0b8d7e921375b43","tid":541950,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:28:18.000Z","msg":"政府今次捉蟲啦 <br />\n收到風周庭公投嗰陣會投留喺中國囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00df9f26c146baf0dfed7adbb00010cc4e4a54e","tid":541950,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪臭係"},{"pid":"3bbb6ec3e1a577f3d9a2c4432563441a235b04fd","tid":541950,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f947026da7da4823189d00b2ccad9fa976bbfa9","tid":541950,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"公墓園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0d4732cf81164979ce3bed7b937b25f9c63032","tid":541950,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"選舉主任地位超然"},{"pid":"8f7b08c9c0c4e07ea4b9cda01cc568b34be26b52","tid":541950,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f1aa4c37564d7b91750b5fbc97e2b68c575cf5","tid":541950,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"痴撚線政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c3d2454b150b10ba5046e7b54da9e88948fe42","tid":541950,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:03:48.000Z","msg":"仲忍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47acb7260583a41e1ec90f29a4f23159a5df